text: Kenji Uchino is an electrical engineer at ONR Global's Asia office in Tokyo, Japan. He was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for his contributions to piezoelectric and electrostrictive actuators and electromechanical energy conversion. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Japanese engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
